              <span class="offering__paragraph-emphasis offering__paragraph-emphasis--grey">Memorize</span> the private key! It will be linked to the account that we create for you.
            </p>

            <p class="offering__paragraph offering__paragraph--centered offering__paragraph--fz--md">
              <span class="offering__paragraph-emphasis offering__paragraph-emphasis--grey">Note:</span> The hash from the brain key gives you a private key. The hash of that hash produces a public key. If you lose a public key, you can get it from your private key. If you lose a private one, it can be accessed through the brain key.
