<div class="container-fluid instructions">
  <div class="row instruction">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 instruction__content">

        <p class="instruction__paragraph">
          Now you need to import your private key:
        </p>

        <pre class="instruction__code"><code class="instruction__code-content"><span class="instruction__code-line">>> import_key my-very-new-account &lt;your private here&gt;</span></code></pre>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid instructions">
  <div class="row instruction">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 instruction__content">

        <p class="instruction__paragraph">
          To check the balance in all your accounts, you can do the following:
        </p>

        <pre class="instruction__code"><code class="instruction__code-content"><span class="instruction__code-line">unlocked >>> list_account_balances my-very-new-account, 1</span></code></pre>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid instructions">
  <div class="row instruction">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 instruction__content">

        <p class="instruction__paragraph">
          You’ve nailed it! With a functioning account, it is easy to become a witness. Here is how you can do that:
        </p>

        <pre class="instruction__code"><code class="instruction__code-content"><span class="instruction__code-line">unlocked >>> create_witness my-very-new-account "https://flacon.array.io" true</span></code></pre>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid instructions">
